@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hhbebo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.15 / tmp + 0.13)) + ((tmp + 0.12 - v2 + 0.78) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.91)))
    tmp = (0.22 - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.41) - (tmp + 0.77 / v0 + 0.52)))
    v2 = 0.34
    v0 = (0.02 + (wp.exp(v0 + 0.65) / (v2 + 0.79 + v1 + 0.14)))
    data[tid] = v0
